# Machine state: post-fold KBs keep everything under one `mage/.mage/` home (ADR-0025).
# This repo predates the fold — its (still-0.0.11) hooks write the legacy top-level dirs
# until the binary is upgraded and `mage migrate` relocates them — so keep BOTH ignored
# (the legacy lines are harmless once those dirs are gone).
mage/.learnings/
mage/.metrics/
mage/.staging/
mage/.mage/
# `mage connect` writes an advisory .bak beside the (already-ignored) local settings.
.claude/settings.local.json.bak
